               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370814-name-983" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-983" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-983" type="surname" value="STEPPINGS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-983" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS STEPPINGS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a green-grocer, and live in Clare-market. I rent the house—George Cullam Marchant and others are the landlords—the lead pipe was all safe, fixed in the passage between the two kitchens, and on the 6th of August, about eight o'clock in the evening, I was sent for, as the water was running very fast—I went home, and in going down the stairs I met the prisoner with the pipe—I took him into custody—we have lost a great deal of pipe lately.</p>
               <p>
